## Components

### User Interface
- **Jupyter Notebook**: Interactive learning environment
- **PySpark API**: Python interface to Spark
- **Spark SQL**: SQL interface for structured queries

### Spark Core
- **Spark Core**: Distributed processing engine
- **Spark MLlib**: Machine learning library
- **Spark Streaming**: Real-time data processing
- **Spark SQL Engine**: SQL optimization and execution

### Storage Layer
- **MinIO S3**: S3-compatible object storage
- **Local File System**: Local development storage

### Cluster Management
- **Standalone**: Simple cluster manager
- **Docker Compose**: Container orchestration
- **Kubernetes**: Production-grade orchestration
